 as you've probably been able to glean from the capsule, is about rebuilding and opportunity. As JasonA put it, "there's Mana in them thar hills." It's a Mage gold rush. We want to see concepts that embrace that feeling. We'll be getting some squibs to detail the setting in other major CA areas very shortly.%0a%3c %0a%3c * 2 BXP for a compelling NPC created in a backstory, allowed once.%0a%3c * 2 BXP for being a Pentacle Mage.%0a%3c * 2 BXP for being a newcomer to San Diego from another California area or from the Tijuana area/ 1 BXP for being a newcomer from another area in the United States or Northern Mexico.%0a%3c %0a%3c %0a%3c '''Lex Magica:'''\\%0a%3c %0a%3c In order to create a decent body of precedent for the Lex from the start of the game, xp is being offered for writing up individual cases. It should be short, no longer than two paragraphs, and should mention the legal issue at play, the factual circumstances, and the result. We retain discretion to amend any precedents offered, but as long as they aren't flat-out rejected, you'll still get your bonus.%0a%3c %0a%3c * 1 BXP per precedent written, to a max of 3.%0a%3c %0a%3c '''Maximum: +5BXP'''\\%0a%3c %0a%3c [--%25color=#1b9ad0%25[[#mtop| Back to top]]--]\\%0a%3c \\%0a%3c %0a%3c %0a%3c [[#UpdateThreads]]%0a%3c %25color=#1b9ad0%25[++'''Character Update Threads'''++]\\%0a%3c \\%0a%3c %0a%3c Character Update Threads are a very important part of Wanton Wicked! Character Update Threads allow players to communicate with STs, leave records of what there character has done or will do, and request scenes or expenditure of experience points! After you have been sanctioned, create the a thread in the [[http://www.wantonwicked.net/forum/viewforum.php?f=428| Mage Character Threads]] section of the forum with a title in the following format: [Order] ~Shadowname~ First Name Last Name. Remember, this will be your primary method of communicating with the Storytellers so don't forget to check back often!\\%0a%3c %0a%3c [--%